title: For Lease: 14 Wildwood Avenue - Unit 1
posting_body: ['2BR / 1Ba 1,443 +/-ft2', 'For Lease: 14 Wildwood Avenue - Unit 1', 'Arlington, MA 02476-6422, Massachusetts', 'This Apartment features plenty of natural light on the first floor having two sizable bedrooms and one bathroom making you feel right at home!', 'The foyer leads to a spacious living room and full sized dining room.', 'The dining room will serve all your needs from casual to formal dining.', 'Beautiful hardwood floors throughout.', 'You will enjoy cooking in this bright eat-in kitchen, or hang out on your sun porch.', 'For your appliances, there is a gas range, a dishwasher, and refrigerator.', 'Save money and time doing your laundry with a washer and dryer in the basement.', 'Parking for two cars, one in the garage and one on the outside parking spot in front of the overhead garage door.', "Pictures before current tenant's move-in.", ' Just steps away from the MBTA Bus Stop, bike path, shopping, restaurants, parks and many more!.', 'Access to major highways.', 'Come see as to what Arlington has to offer!', "Don't miss out, call to schedule an appointment for a showing!", 'Exclusive Agent:', 'Action Real Estate Brokers, Inc.', '965 Massachusetts Avenue', 'Arlington, MA 02476', 'Phone 781-646-2800', 'Disclaimer: ALL PROPERTY INFO SUBJECT TO CHANGE, and SUITES MAY NO LONGER BE AVAILABLE***', '****Equal Opportunity Housing*****', '****', 'We are currently following CDC protocol and guidance for measures in protection against Covid-19 Coronavirus*****']
